  "remarks": "\nFormer so-called \"Internal affairs minister\" of the \"Donetsk People's Republic\". Associated with Vladimir Antyufeyev, who was responsible for the separatist \"government\" activities of the so called \"Government of the Donetsk People's Republic\". He has therefore supported actions and policies which undermine the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine. The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
